text: Choose one response that best describes how strongly each item applies to you:
Intelligence can increase or decrease depending on whether or not you spend time exercising your mind.
What would be MORE impacted by damage to the RIGHT side of your brain than the LEFT?
Answers: Ability to say "Lesser leather never weathered wetter weather better."|Ability to recognise faces by sight|Multiply 2 X 3 X 4 X 5|Navigate
